ckquote><br />\n補個允<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDjent呢個字原本一種攞㴝形容個種pulm mute 聲(Jent jent 聲)嘅字 係periphery 個結他手自已造嘅字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過後尾直情當左一種genre"},{"pid":"c1d720b7b6b8a9ef5dc8f292b0185415734e191d","tid":41614,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有聽animal as leaders 但都唔太知djent係咩黎<br />\n其實djent姐係點？唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDjent呢個名嘅由來呢 其實好簡單<br />\n<br />\n係因為首歌好多底音 Jent Jent聲<br />\n咁呢啲人就開始叫佢Djent<br />\n就好似你應該聽過嘅Animals As Leaders咁<br />\n佢地大部分歌都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過 最正統形容Animals As Leaders嘅曲風係叫Progressive Metal<br />\n所以我會歸類Progressive Metal係Djent<br />\n不過Djent唔一定係Progressive Metal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名等其他師兄補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實djent唔算係一個genre黎 反而係形容緊個結他tone<br />\n通常係講緊結他palm mute做出黎既jent jent聲同ghost note既d d聲，再加個超強勁noise gate，隻聲set好aggressive咁 出到黎就&ldquo;djent&rdquo;喇<br />\n<br />\ndjent多數都係progressive metal, 但progressive  metal就肯肯定唔等於djent(dream theater一定唔係djent啦)<br />\n<br />\nchon屬於jazz fusions野但都有人話佢地係djent band，polyphia又有人話係djent，總之到而家條線都仲係好模糊 我都唔係好識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之一句講哂 djent野通常都難玩到仆街果堆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a1806af9bd2